{%- comment -%}
  Hero meta-row icons — the real vanuitkracht.nl vacancy icons.
  Shared by: kracht-split-hero (meta row) and kracht-schedule-cards (session rows).
  They inherit currentColor (blue on the meta row) and are sized by CSS
  (height + auto width) so each keeps its own proportions.
  Usage: {% render 'kracht-hero-icon', icon: 'clock' %}
  Options: location, clock (alias: hours), briefcase, euro, users (alias: people)
{%- endcomment -%}
